### Admin API Testing
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjMsInJvbGUiOiJBRE1JTiIsImlhdCI6MTc2NjQyNDQ0NywiZXhwIjoxNzY2NDI1MzQ3fQ.IMTXkoE3OYCrAmzvvOkzJVkm0relHGag6AHWccu83QA

## 1. Create Admin User (Initial Setup)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/admin/create-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+251900000000",
  "email": "admin@et-ticket.com",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User"
}

## 2. Request OTP for Admin
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/otp/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+251900000000"
}

## 3. Verify OTP and Login as Admin
### IMPORTANT: Check the server console for the OTP code, then replace it below
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+251900000000",
  "otp": "REPLACE_WITH_OTP_FROM_CONSOLE"
}

### ⚠️ IMPORTANT: After running step 3 above:
### 1. Look at the response JSON
### 2. Copy the "accessToken" value (the long string after "accessToken": "...")
### 3. Replace YOUR_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN below with that token
### 
### Example response from step 3:
### {
###   "user": { ... },
###   "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",  <-- COPY THIS
###   "refreshToken": "..."
### }

## 4. Get All Users (Admin Only)
### Replace YOUR_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN with the actual token from step 3
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 5. Get Pending Organizers Only
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 6. Approve Organizer
### First run step 5 to get the user ID, then replace USER_ID below
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/USER_ID/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 7. Suspend User (Replace USER_ID)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/USER_ID/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 8. Activate User (Replace USER_ID)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/USER_ID/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 9. Test Admin-Only Route
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjMsInJvbGUiOiJBRE1JTiIsImlhdCI6MTc2NjQyNDAxNCwiZXhwIjoxNzY2NDI0OTE0fQ.Ey7H17l9Fi7u3NI7DqGudQsszTEC2HJZb_q-MAB2fmk

### Troubleshooting:
### - If you get "Unauthorized" error: Make sure you copied the FULL accessToken from step 3
### - If you get "Forbidden" error: The user doesn't have ADMIN role
### - Token expires in 15 minutes - if expired, repeat steps 2-3 to get a new token
